  m_text: 'LHTransitionAnimator is a component that extends LHAnimationClipPlayer
    for scene transitions.


    By integrating it into the base classes of Scene
    and ScreenStack, developers can implement animations without having to worry
    about animation playback.


    Clearly separating the work of junior and senior
    engineers allows for both improved project quality and increased efficiency.'
